		<title>20THE FUTURE</title>
		<content>The class leaving Meir Heath Primary   
School on 26th.July 1985 was asked the 
following question:-                   
"What is your main worry about your    
future?"                               
This is a list of their replies:-      
                                       
Employment ................... 16      
The H Bomb .................... 4      
Passing exams for a good job .. 3      
Computers taking over our lives 1      
Parental relationships ........ 1      
Mum and Dad dying ............. 1      
Drugs ......................... 1      
Paying the rates .............. 1      
Raising a family .............. 1      
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
